item.title: About
item.description: Hey, my name is Fathoor, currently an Information Systems’ student at Institut Teknologi Sepuluh Nopember and is completing bachelor’s degree in Computer Science. I usually goes by the name bebekpakeb, since most people do recognize my nickname better rather than my actual name. Why bebekpakeb? Haha, it’s actually a bit funny that the fact that I chose that name was because bebek, which is ‘duck’ in Bahasa, is one of many other food that I prefer not to eat, yes I prefer not for a specific reason.
